OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloud
OL,6,Fbreaking through the evening, with
OL,7,Fsome late sunny spells. Cloud
OL,8,Fthickening overnight, with a chance of
OL,9,Fisolated light showers. Light winds
OL,10,Fcontinuing. Cold with a chance of
OL,11,Ffrost.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FA cold and rather bright
OL,14,Fstart. Becoming increasingly cloudy
OL,15,Fthrough the morning. Frequent showers
OL,16,Fwill move slowly west in the
OL,17,Fafternoon, these perhaps heavy in
OL,18,Fplaces. Winds remaining light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
